AN ACT making an appropriation to the Division of Public and
Behavioral Health of the Department of Health and
Human Services for carrying out a nurse apprentice
program; and providing other matters properly relating
thereto.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, REPRESENTED IN
SENATE AND ASSEMBLY, DO ENACT AS FOLLOWS:
1 Section 1. 1. There is hereby appropriated from the State
2 General Fund to the Division of Public and Behavioral Health of the
3 Department of Health and Human Services the sum of $12,000,000
4 for carrying out a nurse apprentice program.
5 2. Money appropriated by subsection 1 may be:
6 (a) Granted to another entity to carry out the program.
7 (b) Used only for:
8 (1) Reimbursement of a health care entity that is enrolled in
9 the program for:
10 (I) Compensation paid by the health care entity to each
11 nurse apprentice who participates in the program and is employed
12 by the health care entity;
-
